{"tid":49566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】街頭毆鬥3少女 3休班警被捕","createTime":"2016-12-21T20:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T00:38:58.000Z","uid":59695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3139d91ae293367ef0d16cb485963915c266344e","tid":49566,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:02:10.000Z","msg":"3名休班警涉嫌酒後在街頭與3名少女毆鬥，事後全部人被捕。事發於凌晨3時半左右，4名休班警員，在旺角夜店消遣後帶醉離開，至旺角道28號對開，疑與3名同為22歲的少女踫撞後，一名少女感覺被人觸摸臀部，大怒與其中3警爭執，雙方繼而大打出手，眾人均手部受傷。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將6人拘捕，全部人事後被送廣華醫院治理。<br />\n被捕3名休班警員，分別為40歲姓游、33歲姓潘及31歲姓唐。據悉，他們3人為毒品調查科探員，其中一人為警長。案件交由旺角警區重案組跟進。警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"eb41c131fee298b0e5b58e66b866914a9a207a60","tid":49566,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:03:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56074659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56074659&d=smd8PAPZq11A2qEuW46VUAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=4dd7210d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56074659&h=1ce5bf35\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56074659</a>"},{"pid":"f8762e62564a55249e7bdbc3304735984e02f9b0","tid":49566,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:04:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5c8d490d8cecba0af1059471b2e11fe954ca2a0","tid":49566,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:15:10.000Z","msg":"啊sir做野唔使你教"},{"pid":"341b0d5f3e3f090e9b6829193118ccfae01ca285","tid":49566,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"